_sText:
This is the second version of my new zombie map.

The map is a recreation of a swimming facility.

If you have any feedback, please share!

To be able to play this map, download the .rar file and extract the .bsp file to your maps folder in the download folder (inside cstrike).

------------------v1_1 updates---------------------
#Added more spawns (on request), 64 now
#Fixed buyzones
#Added another big room with a catamaran in it
#Started optimization (fixed many func_details + area portals)
#Fixed elevator
#Added two smaler hideouts/rooms
#Removed lag-causing physics
